  <brief_title>Low Dose Cyclosporin A in Primary Sjögren Syndrome</brief_title>
  <acronym>CYPRESS</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase II Pilot-Study With Low-dose Sandimmun Optoral (Cyclosporin A) for the Treatment of Primary Sjögren Syndrome</official_title>
