    <measure>Examination of the therapeutic effects (improvement in number of tender, swolen joints, DAS 28) of low dose Cyclosporine A in patients with primary Sjögren Syndrome and articular involvement after a treatment-phase of 16 weeks.</measure>
    <time_frame>16 weeks</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
